                               Statutes & Laws

      The Department of Fair Employment and Housing enforces four laws:

                              [clearpixel.gif]

                    Fair Employment & Housing Act (FEHA)
                    California Family Rights Act (CFRA)
                    Unruh Civil Rights Act
                    Ralph Civil Rights Act

